Hanif Decision Synthesis.

This recipe mixes raw optimization with ethical weight to produce a balanced Hanif decision.

Ingredients.
101 g efficiency
88 g fıtrat principles
1 ml conscience spark

Method.
Put efficiency into the mixing bowl.
Add fıtrat principles into the mixing bowl.
Fold in the conscience spark.
Stir the mixing bowl until smooth.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
